text: haey nowpel del banda anak mean chomnue bankheunh aah hsaa b( breachy) puokke niyeay tha nih kuchea avei del a l laoh ning anakneasar robsa trong ban sanyea champoh puok yeung . haey a l laoh ning anakneasar robsa trong ban brab kuchea karpit . haey kmeanoavei them dl puokke krawpi kar chuecheak ning kar braklkhluon noh laey
